---
import LegalLayout from '../../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../../config/site';
import { webPageJsonLd } from '../../lib/seo';

const title = 'Disclaimer — FreeIQCheck';
const description = `Disclaimer for ${site.domain}. Free IQ test for education and entertainment only—not a clinical, medical, or diagnostic assessment.`;
---

<LegalLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  path="/disclaimer"
  heading="Disclaimer"
  jsonLd={[webPageJsonLd(title, description, '/disclaimer')]}
>
  <p>
    Please read this Disclaimer carefully before using <a href={site.url}>FreeIQCheck</a> ({site.domain}). By using our website, quiz,
    blog, or related content, you acknowledge and agree to the statements below.
  </p>

  <h2>Not a clinical or medical IQ test</h2>
  <p>
    FreeIQCheck is <strong>not</strong> an official psychological, psychiatric, or medical intelligence test. We are not a licensed
    testing organization, hospital, or clinic. Our 25-question logical reasoning quiz produces an <strong>illustrative score</strong> for
    education and entertainment—it is not a normed IQ score suitable for diagnosis, treatment, employment screening, gifted program
    placement, or legal proceedings.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you need formal cognitive assessment, consult a qualified psychologist or other licensed professional who administers validated
    instruments under controlled conditions.
  </p>

  <h2>No professional advice</h2>
  <p>
    All content on this site—including articles, guides, blog posts, FAQs, score explanations, and emails—is provided for general
    informational purposes only. It does not constitute medical advice, mental health advice, legal advice, or career counseling.
  </p>
  <p>Never disregard professional advice or delay seeking it because of something you read on FreeIQCheck.</p>

  <h2>Accuracy and limitations of results</h2>
  <p>
    Quiz outcomes depend on question selection, timing, your physical and mental state, device, and scoring methodology. Illustrative
    IQ-style numbers and percentile estimates on our results page are <strong>not</strong> population-normed and may differ substantially
    from scores on professional batteries such as WAIS, WISC, or Stanford-Binet.
  </p>
  <p>
    We make reasonable efforts to provide clear explanations and fair-weighted scoring, but we do <strong>not</strong> guarantee
    accuracy, completeness, or fitness for any particular purpose.
  </p>

  <h2>Educational and entertainment use only</h2>
  <p>FreeIQCheck is intended for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Curiosity and self-directed learning</li>
    <li>Practicing logical reasoning and puzzle formats</li>
    <li>Comparing your own retakes over time for personal motivation</li>
  </ul>
  <p>It is <strong>not</strong> intended for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Clinical diagnosis of intellectual disability or giftedness</li>
    <li>Employment or insurance decisions</li>
    <li>Academic admissions or scholarship eligibility</li>
    <li>Establishing legal competence or disability status</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Advertising disclosure</h2>
  <p>
    FreeIQCheck may display third-party advertisements, including Google AdSense. We may earn revenue when visitors view or interact with
    ads. Advertisers are independent third parties; we do not control ad content and are not responsible for products or services
    advertised.
  </p>
  <p>
    Editorial content—including articles about IQ scores, accuracy, and improvement—is written for education and is not influenced by
    advertisers. See our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for cookie and ad personalization information.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-party links and tools</h2>
  <p>
    Our site may link to external websites (e.g., Google opt-out pages, reference materials). We are not responsible for the content,
    privacy practices, or availability of third-party sites. Use them at your own risk.
  </p>
  <p>
    We use third-party services such as Google Analytics and hosting providers. Their processing of data is described in our Privacy
    Policy.
  </p>

  <h2>No warranties</h2>
  <p>
    THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED &quot;AS IS&quot; WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND. WE DISCLAIM ALL WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING
    MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT.
  </p>

  <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
  <p>
    TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, FREEIQCHECK SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES ARISING FROM YOUR USE OF OR RELIANCE ON THE
    QUIZ, SCORES, OR CONTENT, INCLUDING DIRECT, INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES.
  </p>

  <h2>Children and vulnerable users</h2>
  <p>
    Parents and guardians should supervise minors using online quizzes. Results should not be used to label or limit a child&apos;s
    potential. For developmental or educational concerns, seek guidance from qualified educators or clinicians.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Disclaimer at any time. The date at the top of this page indicates the latest revision. Continued use constitutes
    acceptance of the updated Disclaimer.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions: <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a> · <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    Related: <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a> · <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> · <a href="/test">Take the quiz</a>
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
